|name=Al-Mustazi
|picture=[[Image:EN Al-Mustazi crater.jpg|250px|]]<br><small>Al-Mustazi (center) as seen<br>by the ''Cassini'' spacecraft on July 14, 2005</small>
|location={{Coord|20.86|S|202.04|W|globe:enceladus|notes=<ref name=USGS/>}}
